  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baf \u0baa\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b95\u0bb2 \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3 \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb3\u0bcd !",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Request to all the politicians of Askriya Faculty!",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Anunayaka Medagama Dhammananda Thera of Askriya Peetha requested that all politicians should put aside their party politics and work with dedication for the country in order to establish political stability and peace in the country.",
        "Medagama Dhammananda Thera said the above in a special announcement issued after Speaker Mahindayapa Abeywardhana officially announced the resignation of President Gotabaya Rajapaksa last Friday.",
        "The main reason for the intensification of the political crises is the heeding of the advice given by the Maha Sangha to take appropriate measures regarding the situation in the country. Therefore, the leaders of the existing political parties should leave their party politics and act with commitment to the country.",
        "Therefore, we request you to take legal and constitutional steps to establish political and economic stability and peace in the country.",
        "He said that we request the politicians on behalf of all Mahasangham members to work with dedication."
      ],
